FORMER MANQOBA "SHAKES"NGWENYA & GENERAL SIPHIWE NYANDA HAVE A VERY INTERESTING STORY... Not a lot of people in Mzansi know that former Minister of Communication General Siphiwe Nyanda is Manqoba "Shakes" Ngwenya's malume. Nicknamed Ghebuza, Nyanda is a decorated armed struggle freedom fighter. He served as Chiefs of the South African National Defence Force from 1998-2005. "Shakes" was a darling of Bidvest Wits and Sundowns with his precision passes and darting runs across the field. He also played for Bafana Bafana.